b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":764,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Slowdowns for Certain Devices in the Fractured Futures Raid Event","message":"<div>We have confirmed an issue where the game sometimes runs slowly on certain devices in the Fractured Futures raid event, which went live <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1569823200\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>If your game is running slowly, changing Visual Effects to Basic and Image Quality to Normal under Graphic Settings and disabling the combat log can mitigate the issue, so please try that.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Follow the steps below to change your settings:<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>1. Tap More on the in-game footer menu.<\/div><div>2. Tap Options.<\/div><div>3. Select the Game tab.<\/div><div>4. Under Graphic Settings, set Visual Effects to Basic, and set Image Quality to Normal.<\/div><div>5. Under Combat Log Settings, set the combat log to off.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1569823200,"prev_article_id":"779","next_article_id":"777","image_path":"","update_time":1569489416}}}'